      Press release
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    UK announces £1m towards the international response for people affected by the typhoon and extreme flooding in Southeast Asia
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">UK aid will help provide food, clean water and shelter to people affected by Typhoon Goni in the Philippines and extreme flooding in Vietnam. </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
